<item>
            <title>[CAMEL-6168] SQL component will not look for parameters in header when no body in message</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CAMEL-6168</link>
                <project id="12311211" key="CAMEL">Camel</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Line 60 in SqlProducer checks if the body is null. This will cause any parameters in header fields not to be populated into the prepared statement. Sample scenario is with a camel-jetty enriching a response using camel-sql. &lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment>&lt;p&gt;2.11-SNAPSHOT&lt;/p&gt;</environment>
        <key id="12637369">CAMEL-6168</key>
            <summary>SQL component will not look for parameters in header when no body in message</summary>
